{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<math>","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n<p>The top-level element in MathML is <code>&lt;math&gt;</code>. Every valid MathML instance must be wrapped in <code>&lt;math&gt;</code> tags. In addition you must not nest a second <code>&lt;math&gt;</code> element in another, but you can have an arbitrary number of other child elements in it.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"Attributes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In addition to the following attributes, the <code>&lt;math&gt;</code> element accepts any attributes of the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code> element.</p>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"attr-class-id-style\">\n  class, id, style</dt>\n <dd>\n  Provided for use with <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">stylesheets</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-dir\">\n  dir</dt>\n <dd>\n  <span class=\"hidden\">&nbsp;</span>Overall directionality of formulas. Possible values are either <code>ltr</code> (left to right) or <code>rtl</code> (right to left).</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-href\">\n  href</dt>\n <dd>\n  Used to set a hyperlink to a specified URI.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathbackground\">\n  mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>\n  The background color. You can use <code>#rgb</code>, <code>#rrggbb</code> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">HTML color names</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathcolor\">\n  mathcolor</dt>\n <dd>\n  The text color. You can use <code>#rgb</code>, <code>#rrggbb</code> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">HTML color names</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-display\">\n  display</dt>\n <dd>\n  This enumerated attribute specifies how the enclosed MathML markup should be rendered. It can have one of the following values:\n  <ul>\n   <li><code>block</code>, which means that this element will be displayed outside the current span of text, as a block that can be positioned anywhere without changing the meaning of the text;</li>\n   <li><code>inline</code>, which means that this element will be displayed inside the current span of text, and cannot be moved out of it without changing the meaning of that text.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>If not present, its default value is <code>inline</code>.</p>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mode\">\n  mode <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>\n  Deprecated in favor of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math#attr-display\">display attribute</a>.<br>\n  Possible values are: <code>display</code> (which has the same effect as <code>display=\"block\"</code>) and <code>inline</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-overflow\">\n  overflow</dt>\n <dd>\n  Specifies how an expression behaves if it is too long to fit in the allowed width.<br>\n  Possible values are: <code>linebreak</code> (default), <code>scroll</code>, <code>elide</code>, <code>truncate</code>, <code>scale</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p><img alt=\"Theorem of Pythagoras\" src=\"/files/3157/math.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html5_notation","title":"HTML5 notation","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>MathML in HTML5<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>a<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>+<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>b<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>=<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>c<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"xhtml_notation","title":"XHTML notation","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span> <span class=\"token name\">PUBLIC</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.1 plus MathML 2.0//EN\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.w3.org/Math/DTD/mathml2/xhtml-math11-f.dtd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>MathML in XHTML<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>a<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>+<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>b<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>=<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>c<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Notes</strong>: XHTML documents with MathML must be served as <code>application/xhtml+xml</code>. You can achieve that easily by adding the <code>.xhtml</code> extension to your local files. For Apache servers you can <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://httpd.apache.org/docs/2.2/mod/mod_mime.html#addtype\" rel=\" noopener\">configure your <code>.htaccess</code> file</a> to map extensions to the correct Mime type. Since you notate your MathML in an XML document, also be sure you write a well-formed XML document.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Feature</th>\n    <th>Chrome</th>\n    <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n    <th>Opera</th>\n    <th>Safari</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>XHTML notation</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> (24 only)</td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>9.5</td>\n    <td>5.1</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>HTML5 notation</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> (24 only)</td>\n    <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>5.1</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>dir</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/12\" title=\"Released on 2012-04-24.\">12.0</a> (12.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>href</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> <a rel=\"external noopener\" href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=85733\" class=\"external\" title=\"\">WebKit bug 85733</a></td>\n    <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/7\" title=\"Released on 2011-09-26.\">7.0</a> (7.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> <a rel=\"external noopener\" href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=85733\" class=\"external\" title=\"\">WebKit bug 85733</a></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>mathbackground</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> (24 only)</td>\n    <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>5.1</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>mathcolor</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> (24 only)</td>\n    <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>5.1</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>overflow</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Feature</th>\n    <th>Android</th>\n    <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n    <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>IE Mobile</th>\n    <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n    <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>XHTML notation</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>HTML5 notation</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>dir</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>12.0 (12.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>href</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>7.0 (7.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>mathbackground</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>mathcolor</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>overflow</code></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko-specific_notes","title":"Gecko-specific notes","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Gecko 7.0 (Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4) introduced support for accepting all MathML attributes on the top-level math element (i.e. the same behavior as a <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code> element). However, the <code>displaystyle</code> attribute was not taken into account and <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=669719\" rel=\" noopener\">has been added</a> in Gecko 8.0 (Firefox 8.0 / Thunderbird 8.0 / SeaMonkey 2.5).</p>\n<p>A textual fall-back (<code>alttext</code>) or referring to an alternative image using the attributes <code>altimg</code>, <code>altimg-width</code>, <code>altimg-height</code> or <code>altimg-valign</code> is currently not implemented in Gecko.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter2.html#interf.toplevel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'The Top-Level math Element' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter7.html#interf.toplevel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'The Top-Level math Element' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>HTML top-level element: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/html\"><code>&lt;html&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li>SVG top-level element: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li>MathML browser test: For <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://www.eyeasme.com/Joe/MathML/MathML_browser_test\" rel=\" noopener\">XHTML</a> and <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://eyeasme.com/Joe/MathML/HTML5_MathML_browser_test\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attributes","id":"attributes"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The top-level element in MathML is <math>. Every valid MathML instance must be wrapped in <math> tags. In addition you must not nest a second <math> element in another, but you can have an arbitrary number of other child elements in it.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<math>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<math>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<math>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"math","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<math>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<math>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<math>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/mathml/element/math","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/mathml/element/math/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML element reference"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math","title":"<math>"}],"pageTitle":"<math> - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}